      <data key="d2">EMP_EMAIL_UK is a unique constraint on the EMAIL column in HR.EMPLOYEES, preventing duplicate email addresses and ensuring unique contact and login credentials.&lt;SEP&gt;EMP_EMAIL_UK is a unique key constraint ensuring that the EMAIL field in the HR.EMPLOYEES table contains unique, non-duplicate email addresses.</data>
