      <data key="d2">EMP_JOB_FK is a foreign key constraint ensuring employee job roles exist by linking JOB_ID in HR.EMPLOYEES to JOBS.JOB_ID.&lt;SEP&gt;EMP_JOB_FK is a foreign key constraint linking the JOB_ID field in HR.EMPLOYEES to the JOBS.JOB_ID field, enforcing referential integrity for job roles.</data>
