      <data key="d2">EMP_MANAGER_FK is a self-referencing foreign key constraint linking MANAGER_ID in HR.EMPLOYEES to EMPLOYEE_ID in the same table, maintaining valid manager references.&lt;SEP&gt;EMP_MANAGER_FK is a self-referencing foreign key constraint linking MANAGER_ID to EMPLOYEE_ID within HR.EMPLOYEES, supporting hierarchical reporting.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-ec5fba35ba0e1ea8c8f5b0c89a38d27d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df7f1caa97c6b4dd058dd6c5d8c8cc76</data>
