      <data key="d2">EMP_DEPT_FK is a foreign key constraint enforcing valid department assignments by linking DEPARTMENT_ID in HR.EMPLOYEES to DEPARTMENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID.&lt;SEP&gt;EMP_DEPT_FK is a foreign key constraint linking DEPARTMENT_ID in HR.EMPLOYEES to DEPARTMENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID, associating employees with departments.</data>
