    <node id="CITY">
      <data key="d0">CITY</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">CITY is a column in the LOCATIONS table representing city names, indexed by LOC_CITY_IX to improve query performance for city-based searches and sorting.&lt;SEP&gt;CITY is a mandatory column in the LOCATIONS table that records the city where the location is situated.&lt;SEP&gt;CITY is a mandatory field in the HR.LOCATIONS table representing the city name of a location, used in queries and geographic reporting.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-f863663ead003b009e2b4af32de47158&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1164983175b10bbf01dc0af45ebb0360&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b70313252212b24335f3373f61fa80d1</data>
