      <data key="d0">STATE_PROVINCE</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">STATE_PROVINCE is a column in the LOCATIONS table that stores state or province codes or names, used for regional identification and query filtering.&lt;SEP&gt;STATE_PROVINCE is a column in the LOCATIONS table that stores the state or province of the location. It is nullable.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1164983175b10bbf01dc0af45ebb0360&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38310d95744bbc5c98b7150c7d4a14b6</data>
