    <node id="JHIST_DEPT_FK">
      <data key="d0">JHIST_DEPT_FK</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">JHIST_DEPT_FK is a foreign key constraint in HR.JOB_HISTORY that references DEPARTMENT_ID in HR.DEPARTMENTS to link job history to departments, nullable to allow missing department info.&lt;SEP&gt;JHIST_DEPT_FK is a foreign key constraint linking DEPARTMENT_ID in HR.JOB_HISTORY to HR.DEPARTMENTS.DEPARTMENT_ID, associating job history with valid departments; this field is nullable.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-6c187f531b2027607e34d96862df8d99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f121281388b7802bd6c53e774f27760d</data>
