    <node id="Index">
      <data key="d0">Index</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">An index is a database performance optimization structure that improves data retrieval speed, particularly for specific columns in tables.&lt;SEP&gt;An index that enables fast creation and access, supporting business processes with efficient geographic segmentation and reporting, though it compromises some recovery and scalability features.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1d3ed761714af642cb83ced3f86d6fe5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-37aec452f877d0a9f13557a9709c0553</data>
