    <node id="HR.EMP_DETAILS_VIEW">
      <data key="d0">HR.EMP_DETAILS_VIEW</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">HR.EMP_DETAILS_VIEW is a database view within the HR schema that consolidates detailed employee information by joining multiple related tables, providing a comprehensive snapshot of employee data including personal details, job information, department, location, and regional context.&lt;SEP&gt;HR.EMP_DETAILS_VIEW is a read-only, consolidated database view within the HR schema designed to provide a comprehensive and business-friendly representation of employee data by joining multiple base tables such as employees, departments, jobs, locations, countries, and regions. It supports HR reporting, payroll, organizational hierarchy analysis, and location-based employee distribution reports, while ensuring data security through controlled access and read-only restrictions.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9065b661548e2fda446d88c1a5d4a9b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc669b8fd76a2bbd4d405cb958121319</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753912987</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Employees Table">
      <data key="d0">Employees Table</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The Employees table is a base table within the HR schema containing detailed employee records, including attributes like salary, job title, and manager relationships.&lt;SEP&gt;The Employees table within the HR schema stores employee-specific data such as employee ID, job ID, manager ID, department ID, first and last names, salary, and commission percentage.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9065b661548e2fda446d88c1a5d4a9b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc669b8fd76a2bbd4d405cb958121319</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753912987</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Departments Table">
      <data key="d0">Departments Table</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The Departments table is a base table within the HR schema that stores information about organizational departments, used for grouping and reporting employee data.&lt;SEP&gt;The Departments table within the HR schema contains department-related data including department ID, department name, and location ID.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9065b661548e2fda446d88c1a5d4a9b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc669b8fd76a2bbd4d405cb958121319</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753912987</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Jobs Table">
      <data key="d0">Jobs Table</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The Jobs table is a base table within the HR schema that contains job titles and related job information for employees.&lt;SEP&gt;The Jobs table within the HR schema holds job-related information such as job ID and job title.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9065b661548e2fda446d88c1a5d4a9b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc669b8fd76a2bbd4d405cb958121319</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753912987</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Locations Table">
      <data key="d0">Locations Table</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The Locations table is a base table within the HR schema that holds geographic location data relevant to employees and departments.&lt;SEP&gt;The Locations table within the HR schema includes location data such as location ID, city, state or province, and country ID.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9065b661548e2fda446d88c1a5d4a9b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc669b8fd76a2bbd4d405cb958121319</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753912987</data>
    </node>
    <node id="Countries Table">
      <data key="d0">Countries Table</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">The Countries table is a base table within the HR schema that stores country-level geographic data linked to locations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Countries table within the HR schema contains country data including country ID, country name, and region ID.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9065b661548e2fda446d88c1a5d4a9b7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc669b8fd76a2bbd4d405cb958121319</data>
