    <node id="Constraints and Validation">
      <data key="d0">Constraints and Validation</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Constraints and Validation indicate that the index is non-unique, with no explicit filters or function-based indexing, and does not enforce business rules directly.&lt;SEP&gt;Constraints and Validation refer to the absence of explicit constraints on the HR.EMP_MANAGER_IX index itself, with constraints defined on the base table columns.</data>
