    </node>
    <node id="NOLOGGING Option">
      <data key="d0">NOLOGGING Option</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">NOLOGGING is a storage option used in the LOC_COUNTRY_IX index to minimize redo logging during index creation or maintenance, improving performance but requiring careful backup and recovery planning.&lt;SEP&gt;NOLOGGING is an index creation option used by HR.EMP_NAME_IX to minimize redo log generation during index creation or maintenance, improving performance but with potential recovery trade-offs.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d7c88e676a8afc774890f3b5fe6b5e9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f9fdf4c76d1900d14f7ab7687630396</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753913481</data>
    </node>
    <node id="NOCOMPRESS Option">
      <data key="d0">NOCOMPRESS Option</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">NOCOMPRESS is a storage option applied to the LOC_COUNTRY_IX index that disables data compression, optimizing write performance and avoiding compression overhead.&lt;SEP&gt;NOCOMPRESS is an index option used by HR.EMP_NAME_IX that disables data compression, resulting in full storage of index entries and avoiding CPU overhead associated with compression and decompression.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d7c88e676a8afc774890f3b5fe6b5e9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f9fdf4c76d1900d14f7ab7687630396</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753913481</data>
    </node>
    <node id="NOPARALLEL Option">
      <data key="d0">NOPARALLEL Option</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">NOPARALLEL is a storage option used in the LOC_COUNTRY_IX index that disables parallel execution of DML or index operations, reducing resource contention and complexity.&lt;SEP&gt;NOPARALLEL is an index option used by HR.EMP_NAME_IX that disables parallel execution for index operations, ensuring single-threaded processing to reduce resource contention.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d7c88e676a8afc774890f3b5fe6b5e9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f9fdf4c76d1900d14f7ab7687630396</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1753913481</data>
    </node>
