    <node id="HR.EMP_DEPARTMENT_IX">
      <data key="d0">HR.EMP_DEPARTMENT_IX</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">HR.EMP_DEPARTMENT_IX is a database index created on the DEPARTMENT_ID column of the HR.EMPLOYEES table to improve query performance for department-based employee lookups in HR systems.&lt;SEP&gt;HR.EMP_DEPARTMENT_IX is a non-unique, ascending B-tree index on the DEPARTMENT_ID column of the HR.EMPLOYEES table, designed to optimize queries filtering or joining on department identifiers in HR business processes. It features NOLOGGING to reduce redo log generation, NOCOMPRESS for performance, and NOPARALLEL to avoid parallel execution.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-c484da9a0a9ad0591728777ccd6d9bb8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5214e9996fdebc502db15fbc9950f6f7</data>
