      <data key="d2">Security Context refers to the index inheriting the security settings of the HR.EMPLOYEES table, with no explicit security configurations on the index itself.&lt;SEP&gt;The security context inherited by the LOC_COUNTRY_IX index from the hr.LOCATIONS table, governing access and permissions.</data>
