      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">LOC_COUNTRY_IX is a non-unique, ascending B-tree index on the COUNTRY_ID column of the hr.LOCATIONS table, designed to optimize query performance for country-based filtering and joins in HR systems.&lt;SEP&gt;LOC_COUNTRY_IX is an index object created on the hr.LOCATIONS table to improve query performance by enabling efficient filtering and joining on the COUNTRY_ID column.</data>
