      <data key="d0">HR.COUNTRIES</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">The HR.COUNTRIES table stores standardized information about countries relevant to the HR domain, including country identifiers, names, and associated regions, serving as a reference for geographic classification and regional grouping in HR processes.</data>
