      <data key="d0">JOB_TITLE</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">JOB_TITLE is a job attribute used for filtering, sorting, and reporting job roles within HR workflows and user interfaces.&lt;SEP&gt;JOB_TITLE is a mandatory column in the HR.JOBS table representing the official job designation, such as AD_VP or FI_ACCOUNTANT, stored as VARCHAR2(35 BYTE).</data>
