      <data key="d7">HR.JOB_HISTORY optionally references DEPARTMENT_ID to associate job assignments with departments.&lt;SEP&gt;HR.JOB_HISTORY uses DEPARTMENT_ID to associate job history records with departments, allowing nullable values for missing info.&lt;SEP&gt;The JOB_HISTORY table contains the DEPARTMENT_ID column to record department assignments for employees over time.</data>
